name: Mythology CANCER Zodiac
description:
The story of Hercules who got a very difficult task. 
Asked to kill Hydra. Hercules had a hard time fighting Hydra. 
Goddess Hera, One of Hercules' enemies.
Orders a Crab (CANCER) to help Hydra fight Hercules by thrusting its sharp claws into Hercules' legs. 
Hercules is in pain.
